manal \u201cestilario\u201d para el suplemento queer SOY, del diario Pagina/12 y ha sido colaborador en la secci\u00f3n de cultura de los diarios Clar\u00edn, Cr\u00edtica en Buenos Aires y para Universo Centro de Medell\u00edn.", "language": null, "image": "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/raul-trujilllo-2-foto-de-William-Bucholtz.jpg", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#content", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/", "https://www.unsam.edu.ar/", "#", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/", "https://www.unsam.edu.ar/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/textos/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/ambiente/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/amor-y-sexo/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/culturas/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/educacion/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/politica-y-economia/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/politicas-de-generos/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/salud/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/tecnologias/", "https://podcast.revistaanfibia.com/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/talleres/", "https://periodismoperformatico.com/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.cl/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/que-es-anfibia/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/tienda/", "#", "https://twitter.com/revistaanfibia", "https://www.facebook.com/RevistaAnfibia", "https://www.instagram.com/revistaanfibia", "https://www.youtube.com/user/RevistaAnfibia", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/", "https://www.unsam.edu.ar/", "https://twitter.com/revistaanfibia", "https://www.facebook.com/RevistaAnfibia", "https://www.instagram.com/revistaanfibia", "https://www.youtube.com/user/RevistaAnfibia", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/textos/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/ambiente/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/amor-y-sexo/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/culturas/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/educacion/", "https://www.revistaanfibia.com/category/poli